{"tid":2270934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"RTHK : 特朗普聲言將到聯邦最高法院，要求停止點算選票","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:44:00.000Z","uid":362414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf07bff9d87ccd053b28786b8fa801a7816cb164","tid":2270934,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"美國大選仍在點票，多個關鍵搖擺州未有結果，但爭取連任的特朗普聲稱已經勝出，準備好慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮說，在佛羅里達，俄亥俄和得州勝出，而在賓夕法尼亞、威斯康星、密歇根，以及北卡羅來納州表現理想，對他而言已經勝出。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\"></span><br />\n<strong>特朗普又再次在無證據下，質疑郵寄選票構成舞弊，聲言將到聯邦最高法院，要求停止點算這些選票。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的競選團隊批評特朗普計劃訴諸最高法院是瘋狂，律師團隊準備隨時應戰。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558351-20201104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558351-20201104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcytTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=fc5763a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558351-20201104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=512bcd25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558351-20201104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}